OL,3,CHistoric steam railway begins search
OL,4,Cfor new locomotive driver
OL,6,FA steam railway attraction in Cornwall
OL,7,Fis looking for a new locomotive
OL,8,Fdriver, a unique job that rarely comes
OL,9,Fup.
OL,11,FLappa Valley at St Newlyn East near
OL,12,FNewquay attracts 100,000 people each
OL,13,Fyear who come to ride its miniature
OL,14,Ftrains.
OL,16,FThe job is described as an ''extremely
OL,17,Frare and unique opportunity'' to join
OL,18,Fthe attraction as a Locomotive Driver
OL,19,Fand Rolling Stock Fitter.
