OL,3,CHistoric steam railway begins search
OL,4,Cfor new locomotive driver
OL,6,FLappa Valley operates three gauges of
OL,7,Frailway with a combined fleet of 13
OL,8,Flocomotives, with a mix of steam,
OL,9,Fdiesel, petrol and battery powered
OL,10,Fengines.
OL,12,FOperations Manager Ben Harding told
OL,13,FITV News: ''It's safe to say no two
OL,14,Fdays are the same here.
OL,16,F"You could be driving a steam engine
OL,17,Fone day, a diesel engine the next and
OL,18,Fwe've got electric locomotives on our
OL,19,Fsmaller railways in the leisure park.
