OL,3,CHistoric steam railway begins search
OL,4,Cfor new locomotive driver
OL,6,F"It was my dream when I was young and
OL,7,FI think this could be a dream job for
OL,8,Fsomeone.''
OL,10,FHopeful candidates will need previous
OL,11,Frailway experience, and some
OL,12,Fmechanical knowledge.
OL,14,FOther perks of the job include free
OL,15,Ffamily entry to Lappa Valley and a
OL,16,Fdiscount on national railway services.
OL,18,FLappa Valley is celebrating its 50th
OL,19,Fanniversary in 2024, and it says the
OL,20,Frole is part of its ongoing expansion.
